property.description: PDF Viewer based on Mozilla pdf.js
File or URL path to the PDF file
Reference of the document containing the file (not used if file is a URL)

If this value is true (or 1 or yes) and the user has no access to the document to which the PDF file is attached, the PDF file could still be viewed on behalf of the author of the document containing the macro (if that author has access to the containing document obviously).
